%% Sequence: User login & data fetch

sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Browser
  participant CDN
  participant Next as "Next.js (SSR)"
  participant BFF as "Go BFF"
  participant DB as "Database"

  User->>Browser: open app
  Browser->>CDN: request page
  CDN->>Next: SSR page request
  Next->>BFF: fetch /bff/profile (server side)
  BFF->>DB: query user
  DB-->>BFF: return user
  BFF-->>Next: profile data
  Next-->>CDN: rendered page
  CDN-->>Browser: HTML
